## Manual Payment Flow (InstaPay/Vodafone Cash)

### Step 1: Submit Manual Payment Request with Screenshot
# Note: This uses multipart/form-data with file upload
# Cannot be directly tested in .http files - use Postman, curl, or frontend

POST https://localhost:5001/api/manualpayment
Authorization: Bearer {user-token}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

Form fields:
- ContentId: 1
- TransferMethod: 1
- ReferenceNumber: IP20240212123456
- Screenshot: [file] payment-proof.jpg

Note: transferMethod values:
- 1 = InstaPay
- 2 = VodafoneCash

File requirements:
- Type: JPEG, PNG, WebP, or GIF
- Max size: 5 MB

### Step 2: Get My Payment Requests
GET https://localhost:5001/api/manualpayment/my-requests
Authorization: Bearer {user-token}

### Step 3: Admin - Get Pending Requests
GET https://localhost:5001/api/manualpayment/pending?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {admin-token}

### Step 4a: Admin - Approve Payment
PUT https://localhost:5001/api/manualpayment/5/approve
Authorization: Bearer {admin-token}

# No request body needed
# This automatically creates a Purchase record

### Step 4b: Admin - Reject Payment
PUT https://localhost:5001/api/manualpayment/5/reject?reason=Invalid+reference+number
Authorization: Bearer {admin-token}

# Rejection reason is passed as query parameter

