## Testing Workflow

### Complete User Journey:

1. **Register** → POST /api/authentication/register
2. **Login** → POST /api/authentication/login (get token)
3. **Browse Content** → GET /api/content/visible
4. **View Details** → GET /api/content/1

5. **Manual Payment:**
   - Transfer money via InstaPay/Vodafone Cash
   - Take screenshot of transaction
   - Submit request with file upload → POST /api/manualpayment
   - Admin reviews → GET /api/manualpayment/pending
   - Admin approves → PUT /api/manualpayment/{id}/approve
   - Access content → GET /api/content/1/access

6. **View My Purchases** → GET /api/purchase/my-purchases

---

## Error Responses

### Unauthorized (401)
{
  "title": "Unauthorized",
  "status": 401,
  "detail": "You are not authorized to access this resource"
}

### Not Found (404)
{
  "title": "Not Found",
  "status": 404,
  "detail": "Content with ID 999 not found"
}

### Validation Error (400)
{
  "title": "Validation Failed",
  "status": 400,
  "errors": {
    "Title": ["Title is required"],
    "Price": ["Price must be between 0.01 and 100000"]
  }
}

### Access Denied (403)
{
  "title": "Forbidden",
  "status": 403,
  "detail": "You don't have access to this content or your access has expired"
}

