## Testing with cURL

### Create Content (Admin)
```bash
curl -X POST https://localhost:5001/api/content \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "title": "Test Course",
    "description": "Test Description",
    "type": 1,
    "price": 49.99,
    "accessDurationWeeks": 8,
    "youtubeVideoId": "test123",
    "isVisible": true
  }'
```

### Submit Manual Payment with File Upload
```bash
curl -X POST https://localhost:5001/api/manualpayment \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_USER_TOKEN" \
  -F "ContentId=1" \
  -F "TransferMethod=1" \
  -F "ReferenceNumber=IP20240212123456" \
  -F "Screenshot=@/path/to/payment-proof.jpg"
```

### Approve Manual Payment (Admin)
```bash
curl -X PUT https://localhost:5001/api/manualpayment/5/approve \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN"
```

### Reject Manual Payment (Admin)
```bash
curl -X PUT "https://localhost:5001/api/manualpayment/5/reject?reason=Invalid+transaction" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN"
```

