## Testing Notes

### Meeting Link Validation
The system accepts URLs from these providers:
- Zoom: https://zoom.us/j/*
- Google Meet: https://meet.google.com/*
- Microsoft Teams: https://teams.microsoft.com/*
- Webex: https://webex.com/*

### Google Drive URL Auto-Conversion
Input formats automatically converted to embeddable previews:
- https://drive.google.com/file/d/FILE_ID/view → /preview
- https://drive.google.com/file/d/FILE_ID/edit → /preview
- https://drive.google.com/open?id=FILE_ID → /preview

### Authorization Rules
- **Admin**: Full access to all endpoints
- **Instructor**: Can create/edit/delete only their own sessions
- **Student**: Read-only access to enrolled course sessions

### Validation Rules
- Session start time must be before end time
- Meeting link must be a valid URL
- Title max 200 characters
- Description max 2000 characters

