## Course E-Wallet Payment System

### Instructor: Add e-wallet payment method to a course
POST http://localhost:5000/api/instructor/courses/{{courseId}}/payment-methods
Authorization: Bearer {{instructor-token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "methodName": "Vodafone Cash",
  "walletNumber": "01099887766"
}

###

### Instructor: Update payment method
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/instructor/courses/{{courseId}}/payment-methods/1
Authorization: Bearer {{instructor-token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "methodName": "InstaPay",
  "walletNumber": "01234567890"
}

###

### Instructor: Deactivate payment method
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/instructor/courses/{{courseId}}/payment-methods/1
Authorization: Bearer {{instructor-token}}

###

### Instructor: List payment methods for a course
GET http://localhost:5000/api/instructor/courses/{{courseId}}/payment-methods
Authorization: Bearer {{instructor-token}}

###

### Student (or anyone): View available payment methods for a course
GET http://localhost:5000/api/courses/{{courseId}}/payment-methods

###

### Student: Submit payment proof (multipart/form-data)
# 1. Transfer money to the wallet number shown above
# 2. POST this with your screenshot image file
POST http://localhost:5000/api/courses/{{courseId}}/pay
Authorization: Bearer {{student-token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----boundary

------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="eWalletMethodId"

1
------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="studentWalletNumber"

01012345678
------boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="screenshot"; filename="receipt.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./receipt.jpg
------boundary--

###

### Student: View my payment requests
GET http://localhost:5000/api/student/course-payments
Authorization: Bearer {{student-token}}

###

### Admin: View all pending course payment requests
GET http://localhost:5000/api/admin/payments/course/pending
Authorization: Bearer {{admin-token}}

###

### Admin: View all course payment requests (all statuses)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/admin/payments/course/all?pageIndex=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{admin-token}}

###

### Admin: Approve a payment request (auto-enrolls student)
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/admin/payments/course/1/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{admin-token}}

###

### Admin: Reject a payment request
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/admin/payments/course/1/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{admin-token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "approve": false,
  "rejectionReason": "Screenshot is blurry, please resubmit."
}

